This paper discusses the use and development of evolutionary algorithms, which are a type of artificial intelligence technique. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the increasing demand for these techniques, which suggests that it may fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the integration of these techniques into society and human processes, which suggests that it may fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
